WEBVTT

01:51.759 --> 01:57.560
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.560 --> 02:01.780
[Episode 18]

02:02.590 --> 02:03.180
Dad.

02:03.640 --> 02:04.030
Look.

02:04.840 --> 02:05.640
Look.

02:05.640 --> 02:07.840
It looks custom-made for you.

02:08.280 --> 02:09.470
After working hard for so long,

02:09.470 --> 02:11.270
your wish has finally come true.

02:12.540 --> 02:13.290
Coming.

02:17.280 --> 02:17.910
Yun.

02:26.120 --> 02:26.840
Not bad.

02:26.840 --> 02:28.630
Gao Ran has been busy all day

02:28.630 --> 02:30.340
just to cook this meal for you.

02:30.840 --> 02:32.720
-You're so lucky.
-Sit down.

02:32.740 --> 02:33.940
When you were little,

02:33.960 --> 02:35.950
you cried and begged me for a big brother.

02:35.950 --> 02:36.660
Look,

02:36.710 --> 02:39.370
a good brother just dropped
from the sky for you.

02:39.590 --> 02:40.310
You

02:40.310 --> 02:42.370
always get exactly what you wish for.

02:42.620 --> 02:43.750
You are right, Dad.

02:43.770 --> 02:46.030
Where else can I find such a good brother?

02:46.800 --> 02:47.800
Come, come, come!

02:48.590 --> 02:50.000
Yun's official career

02:50.000 --> 02:51.710
officially begins today.

02:52.380 --> 02:54.030
Come, we must celebrate properly.

02:54.030 --> 02:54.829
Pour the wine!

02:59.260 --> 03:00.690
-Gao Ran.
-Gao Ran.

03:00.820 --> 03:02.570
Gao Ran, where is the wine?

03:04.030 --> 03:04.710
I forgot.

03:04.810 --> 03:06.460
Oh, this child, honestly...

03:08.280 --> 03:09.080
It's fine.

03:09.520 --> 03:11.360
I-I have already received

03:11.360 --> 03:12.960
the kindness from both Gao Ran and Dad.

03:12.960 --> 03:14.430
We'll toast with tea instead of wine.

03:14.430 --> 03:15.520
It's the same.

03:15.520 --> 03:16.560
Good.

03:22.490 --> 03:23.680
What's wrong with you?

03:23.680 --> 03:24.550
Nothing.

03:24.570 --> 03:25.450
Are you sure?

03:25.840 --> 03:26.680
I'm sure.

03:26.750 --> 03:28.590
I'm just here to join in the fun.

03:31.079 --> 03:33.650
[Calmness Before All]

03:43.200 --> 03:44.130
Shi.

03:44.480 --> 03:45.180
Shi.

03:47.000 --> 03:48.760
What time is it?

03:48.790 --> 03:50.320
Why are you still sleeping?

03:53.600 --> 03:56.530
It must be because of your leg injury
from yesterday.

03:58.120 --> 03:59.870
I told you not to kneel and get up.

03:59.870 --> 04:02.110
You insisted on kneeling.

04:02.710 --> 04:04.080
Does your leg hurt?

04:07.400 --> 04:09.060
Did you apply medicine to him?

04:10.380 --> 04:11.370
Master.

04:11.580 --> 04:12.990
Young Master Shi said

04:13.020 --> 04:14.740
this is what he deserves,

04:15.170 --> 04:16.480
so no medicine was applied.

04:16.480 --> 04:17.070
You.

04:17.670 --> 04:18.910
How old is he?

04:19.170 --> 04:21.000
He is too young to know
how to take care of himself.

04:21.000 --> 04:22.079
How old are you?

04:22.100 --> 04:23.500
How could you not know...

04:23.680 --> 04:26.350
How could you not know
to apply some medicine to him?

04:26.350 --> 04:27.470
Go quickly.

04:27.600 --> 04:28.510
I... I know, I know.

04:28.510 --> 04:29.270
Go get the medicine.

04:29.270 --> 04:30.270
I'll go get it now.

04:36.430 --> 04:37.430
Shi.

04:39.190 --> 04:40.950
Listen to Grandfather, Shi.

04:41.070 --> 04:42.070
Master.

04:43.000 --> 04:45.960
Master, calm down!

04:45.980 --> 04:47.390
Raise your head.

04:48.310 --> 04:48.800
Master.

04:49.100 --> 04:50.180
Who are you?

04:50.200 --> 04:50.760
Master.

04:50.790 --> 04:52.120
Who... who... who is he?

04:53.130 --> 04:53.960
He...

04:54.659 --> 04:55.960
Lord Cai requests an audience.

04:55.960 --> 04:56.610
This...

04:58.290 --> 04:59.930
Apply medicine to him quickly.

04:59.930 --> 05:01.370
It's going to...

05:01.390 --> 05:02.660
Why apply medicine to him?

05:02.660 --> 05:03.940
I'm so confused.

05:13.920 --> 05:14.890
Lord Cai,

05:15.920 --> 05:16.820
you are the one

05:17.480 --> 05:20.810
in charge of the probation
for the newly selected scholars.

05:21.480 --> 05:24.170
We appreciate your hard work
these past days.

05:25.270 --> 05:27.680
Thank you for your consideration,
Lord Zheng.

05:27.680 --> 05:31.280
I shall spare no effort
to select talents for the Nine Cities.

05:32.830 --> 05:34.390
You need to select

05:35.159 --> 05:37.240
the real talents.

05:39.600 --> 05:41.060
You are right, Lord Zheng.

05:42.390 --> 05:43.450
But

05:43.640 --> 05:46.130
this year is very different from the past.

05:46.620 --> 05:48.200
As it's the first time
commoners are taking the exams,

05:48.200 --> 05:51.450
some rumors and criticisms are inevitable.

05:51.920 --> 05:54.190
After all,
this year's scholars are different,

05:54.190 --> 05:55.390
there are commoners,

05:55.980 --> 05:57.390
and even

05:57.409 --> 05:59.380
women recommended for office.

06:05.280 --> 06:08.190
Well, this does follow governor's wishes,

06:08.270 --> 06:10.920
bringing a lot of

06:10.920 --> 06:12.680
fresh blood to Nine Cities.

06:13.680 --> 06:14.550
Commoners

06:15.240 --> 06:16.970
lack upbringing and heritage.

06:18.190 --> 06:20.680
Most are short-sighted.

06:22.460 --> 06:25.330
They are easily blinded by vanity.

06:25.670 --> 06:27.010
And women

06:27.240 --> 06:29.100
will get married sooner or later.

06:29.790 --> 06:32.040
None of them are fit for officialdom.

06:35.440 --> 06:37.470
You are right, Lord Zheng.

06:37.490 --> 06:40.220
So I came to visit you today

06:40.240 --> 06:43.140
to hear your opinion.

06:43.630 --> 06:45.890
How should we treat these

06:46.490 --> 06:47.970
exceptions?

06:50.550 --> 06:51.960
No special treatment.

06:53.630 --> 06:55.480
Just give them no advantages,

06:56.750 --> 06:58.390
let them see

06:59.310 --> 07:01.430
the cruelty of officialdom.

07:03.800 --> 07:05.850
Lord Zheng is absolutely right.

07:05.900 --> 07:08.980
Flowers that have always lived indoors

07:09.020 --> 07:12.020
naturally cannot withstand
the ravages of the storm.

07:12.870 --> 07:14.070
Withering

07:14.070 --> 07:15.950
is only a matter of time.

07:46.240 --> 07:47.430
See? I was right.

07:48.040 --> 07:50.440
Women's clothing really suits you better.

07:53.310 --> 07:54.570
I read your exam paper.

07:55.159 --> 07:56.800
Your answers were very insightful.

07:56.800 --> 07:57.630
So,

07:58.600 --> 08:00.260
was it really just for freedom

08:00.390 --> 08:02.120
that you deliberately failed?

08:03.410 --> 08:04.710
To achieve peace in the world,

08:04.710 --> 08:06.770
being an official is not the only way.

08:06.950 --> 08:08.600
Nine Cities seems peaceful,

08:08.600 --> 08:10.190
but the governor has little power,

08:10.190 --> 08:12.520
and the nobles each rule their own domain.

08:12.670 --> 08:13.850
If Nine Cities is failing,

08:13.850 --> 08:16.130
what good is being an official?

08:16.720 --> 08:18.430
You'd be nothing but a fallen leaf

08:18.430 --> 08:20.360
caught in the struggle
between the governor and the nobles,

08:20.360 --> 08:21.890
drifting without control.

08:22.070 --> 08:24.070
Better to be a free merchant with me.

08:24.200 --> 08:25.410
As long as you follow me,

08:25.410 --> 08:27.520
no matter your standing,
your birth, your past,

08:27.520 --> 08:29.390
I can guarantee you a comfortable life.

08:29.390 --> 08:30.390
Isn't that a million times better

08:30.390 --> 08:32.049
than being a puppet governor?

08:33.179 --> 08:34.760
If you leave the officialdom,

08:34.760 --> 08:36.419
I can promise you a smooth path,

08:36.419 --> 08:37.270
peace and joy.

08:38.020 --> 08:39.250
Anything you want to do,

08:39.250 --> 08:40.650
I can help you achieve it.

08:43.549 --> 08:45.080
Second Young Master Zheng.

08:45.440 --> 08:46.240
If everyone

08:46.870 --> 08:48.530
only looks out for themselves

08:48.790 --> 08:50.240
then no one can survive.

08:51.000 --> 08:52.120
Nine Cities is so big.

08:52.120 --> 08:53.320
As a minor female official on probation,

08:53.320 --> 08:54.480
how far can you go?

08:55.050 --> 08:55.900
Don't forget,

08:56.000 --> 08:57.500
you're not like the other new scholars.

08:57.500 --> 08:59.430
You could be dismissed at any time.

09:01.300 --> 09:02.610
I can't control others,

09:02.610 --> 09:04.230
but I can guarantee that
the people in Juyun Pavilion

09:04.230 --> 09:05.910
won't be burdened by the world,

09:05.910 --> 09:07.260
and will be well-fed and well-clothed.

09:07.260 --> 09:08.770
But have you ever considered

09:08.770 --> 09:10.140
both the selection exam and the governor

09:10.140 --> 09:11.740
can improve people's lives?

09:12.480 --> 09:14.410
And I cannot stand by and do nothing

09:14.580 --> 09:17.380
about any person or thing
that stands in their way.

09:20.960 --> 09:22.870
Do your duty in the position you hold.

09:22.870 --> 09:24.130
We can be rivals,

09:24.260 --> 09:25.650
and we can also be friends.

09:25.650 --> 09:27.630
Even if we stand on different sides,

09:27.630 --> 09:29.000
that doesn't stop us
from talking about music

09:29.000 --> 09:29.870
and life.

09:29.870 --> 09:30.800
Don't you agree?

09:40.320 --> 09:40.920
All right.

09:41.960 --> 09:42.790
Anyway,

09:43.210 --> 09:44.600
thank you for

09:44.620 --> 09:46.190
being honest with me today.

09:47.790 --> 09:48.630
If one day,

09:49.100 --> 09:50.690
because of where we stand,

09:51.360 --> 09:53.760
we find ourselves on opposite sides,

09:54.960 --> 09:55.750
then I...

09:59.080 --> 10:00.150
I...

10:01.350 --> 10:03.150
-I hope that never happens.
-No.

10:04.320 --> 10:06.480
I will never stand against you.

10:16.150 --> 10:17.270
Are you

10:17.290 --> 10:18.530
really not going to consider

10:18.530 --> 10:20.130
joining our Juyun Pavilion?

10:23.560 --> 10:24.220
No. I am not.

10:28.360 --> 10:30.020
You don't have to do anything.

10:35.370 --> 10:37.370
Young Master, please have some tea.

10:49.210 --> 10:50.560
My dear young master,

10:50.670 --> 10:52.070
where have you been?

10:53.240 --> 10:54.570
Grandfather found out?

10:54.720 --> 10:57.080
The Master was worried
kneeling yesterday hurt your health.

10:57.080 --> 10:58.000
He came back and went straight to see you

10:58.000 --> 10:59.390
without even entering his own room.

10:59.390 --> 11:00.840
But you weren't there.

11:01.020 --> 11:01.980
He was so angry

11:02.080 --> 11:03.880
that he didn't even have dinner.

11:11.720 --> 11:12.720
You may go.

11:12.740 --> 11:14.100
I'll go see Grandfather

11:14.130 --> 11:15.390
to offer my apologies.

11:34.260 --> 11:36.100
Grandfather, look what this is.

11:43.190 --> 11:45.390
Won't you open it and see, Grandfather?

12:02.100 --> 12:04.210
I know you and Lord Lyu are good friends.

12:04.210 --> 12:06.670
No one was more heartbroken than you
when the jade button broke.

12:06.670 --> 12:07.320
So I specifically

12:07.320 --> 12:09.820
asked the best restorer
in Ling'an to repair it.

12:09.820 --> 12:11.880
I guarantee it won't damage the jade.

12:15.970 --> 12:17.500
It was just finished today.

12:17.510 --> 12:19.000
I went out just to get it.

12:20.000 --> 12:20.800
Grandfather,

12:22.360 --> 12:23.870
don't be angry.

12:27.350 --> 12:29.870
Who? Who said I care about that thing?

12:30.480 --> 12:32.080
If it's broken, it's broken.

12:32.670 --> 12:34.870
Who cares about that old man's stuff?

12:37.360 --> 12:38.960
You're right, Grandfather.

12:39.200 --> 12:40.870
Since it's a broken thing,

12:41.510 --> 12:43.170
we don't care about it either.

12:43.240 --> 12:44.240
I'll take it away.

12:45.060 --> 12:46.330
Shi... Shi... Shi.

12:48.880 --> 12:50.480
What's wrong, Grandfather?

12:51.030 --> 12:51.940
Nothing.

12:51.960 --> 12:52.690
I'm leaving.

12:52.710 --> 12:54.280
Well... Well, you...

12:55.290 --> 12:56.350
I heard from the butler

12:56.350 --> 12:59.210
that a batch of ingredients
arrived from Jing City.

12:59.380 --> 13:00.640
I'm hungry.

13:01.120 --> 13:02.870
I haven't eaten yet.

13:03.630 --> 13:05.890
Can you have dinner with me?

13:06.120 --> 13:06.720
Of course.

13:10.000 --> 13:11.800
Come, Grandfather. Be careful.

13:34.000 --> 13:34.670
Fan Xiu.

13:34.670 --> 13:35.390
Lord Jiang.

13:36.000 --> 13:36.840
Lord Wang.

13:39.200 --> 13:39.790
Fan Xiu,

13:40.630 --> 13:41.440
what is it?

13:42.120 --> 13:42.780
Lord Jiang,

13:43.200 --> 13:45.260
I am able to serve as an official today

13:46.370 --> 13:47.800
thanks to your support.

13:48.390 --> 13:49.910
The Fan Xiu I know

13:50.320 --> 13:52.320
is a highly motivated young person.

13:53.240 --> 13:54.540
I hope she will

13:54.870 --> 13:57.930
do more good deeds
that benefit the city and its people.

13:59.720 --> 14:00.270
Yes.

14:08.840 --> 14:09.510
Fan Yun?

14:11.150 --> 14:11.910
Governor.

14:13.630 --> 14:15.390
Why are you and Tian Xing still here?

14:15.390 --> 14:17.320
The probation ceremony is about to start.

14:17.320 --> 14:18.650
You are going to be late.

14:19.270 --> 14:20.070
-Late?
-Late?

14:21.460 --> 14:22.070
But...

14:22.090 --> 14:22.690
Follow me.

14:24.040 --> 14:24.680
Tian Xing.

14:24.790 --> 14:25.360
Hurry up!

14:27.180 --> 14:28.410
I'll take you through a shortcut.

14:28.410 --> 14:29.940
We should be able to make it.

14:30.760 --> 14:32.010
Who on earth did this?

14:32.110 --> 14:33.480
They actually changed the time.

14:33.480 --> 14:35.720
I thought the future would be bright.

14:35.720 --> 14:36.360
But who knew

14:36.360 --> 14:38.490
there would be obstacles everywhere.

14:38.840 --> 14:40.320
Thank goodness the governor is here.

14:40.320 --> 14:40.850
Hurry up.

14:41.360 --> 14:42.000
Okay.

14:43.600 --> 14:44.600
Hurry, Tian Xing.

14:47.670 --> 14:48.670
Congratulations to all

14:48.670 --> 14:50.130
newly selected scholars.

14:50.870 --> 14:52.870
According to our Bureau's customs,

14:53.280 --> 14:54.720
all new scholars

14:55.240 --> 14:57.220
must serve here

14:57.390 --> 14:58.920
for a two-month probation.

14:59.240 --> 15:00.870
Although time is limited,

15:01.270 --> 15:02.440
I hope everyone

15:02.440 --> 15:04.270
can seize this opportunity.

15:05.480 --> 15:06.910
After two months,

15:06.950 --> 15:09.140
[Lu Yan,
Deputy Officer of the Ceremony Bureau]

15:07.600 --> 15:09.510
based on everyone's abilities,

15:10.000 --> 15:11.910
you will be officially assigned

15:11.910 --> 15:13.600
to where you are needed.

15:13.600 --> 15:14.790
During this period,

15:15.630 --> 15:17.760
I will serve as your superior officer.

15:19.360 --> 15:20.550
Back then,

15:20.870 --> 15:22.030
Jeong Yoo Wan,

15:22.750 --> 15:23.880
Jiang Shu,

15:24.120 --> 15:26.170
Fan Hui and other scholars

15:26.370 --> 15:27.300
We finally

15:27.320 --> 15:29.560
-made it here.
-were all gathered here.

15:31.650 --> 15:32.720
I have something for you.

15:32.720 --> 15:33.770
What is it?

15:35.940 --> 15:36.940
Take this.

15:38.600 --> 15:39.550
This is...

15:40.170 --> 15:41.420
This is the Fortune Grass.

15:41.420 --> 15:42.340
Congratulations,

15:42.340 --> 15:44.200
you've finally reached this day.

15:45.480 --> 15:46.540
The Fortune Grass.

15:46.850 --> 15:48.680
It can grow strong

15:48.700 --> 15:50.560
even in the harshest conditions.

15:51.150 --> 15:52.210
I like it very much.

15:52.340 --> 15:53.410
Thank you, Governor.

15:53.410 --> 15:55.140
You two are new to officialdom.

15:55.550 --> 15:57.710
The thing you must beware of
is treacherous hearts.

15:57.710 --> 15:59.910
From now on,
you must learn to face things alone.

15:59.910 --> 16:01.510
I can only help you this once.

16:03.600 --> 16:04.200
Go in now.

16:05.440 --> 16:06.300
We're going in.

16:06.830 --> 16:07.540
Let's go.

16:07.570 --> 16:09.430
Officials who pass the probation

16:09.430 --> 16:11.520
will take part in the new-official parade

16:11.520 --> 16:13.340
to officially meet the people.

16:13.890 --> 16:16.340
I hope you'll all start fresh,

16:16.670 --> 16:18.600
and continue to study diligently.

16:19.000 --> 16:20.840
Regarding this probation,

16:21.200 --> 16:24.000
I look forward to growing together
with all of you.

16:24.320 --> 16:25.390
Arriving so late,

16:25.410 --> 16:27.150
they clearly don't take this seriously.

16:27.150 --> 16:28.680
Women becoming officials?

16:29.240 --> 16:30.720
What kind of
recommendation system is this?

16:30.720 --> 16:31.250
Exactly.

16:31.260 --> 16:33.010
It's just tailor-made for certain people.

16:33.010 --> 16:34.440
Everyone can get...

16:34.460 --> 16:36.790
I don't know what they’re even capable of.

16:38.470 --> 16:40.000
What's going on back there?

16:48.680 --> 16:49.710
What are you arguing about?

16:49.710 --> 16:50.590
Lord Lu,

16:51.160 --> 16:53.300
Fan Yun and Tian Xing were not only late,

16:53.300 --> 16:55.330
but they've been chattering
since they arrived,

16:55.330 --> 16:57.350
disrupting our attention
to your instruction.

16:57.350 --> 16:59.350
I request that you expel them both.

16:59.370 --> 17:01.570
I am ashamed to be associated with them.

17:04.270 --> 17:06.349
Do I need you to tell me how to do my job?

17:12.349 --> 17:13.310
Fan Yun,

17:14.880 --> 17:16.880
don't think that just because you were
once the governor's wife,

17:16.880 --> 17:18.510
you can break the rules.

17:20.200 --> 17:22.069
You are now probationary civil officials,

17:22.069 --> 17:24.079
so you must follow the rules here.

17:24.680 --> 17:25.609
Besides,

17:26.119 --> 17:27.849
you are different from others.

17:28.349 --> 17:29.880
The standards for evaluating you

17:29.880 --> 17:31.280
are naturally stricter.

17:31.830 --> 17:32.310
Yes.

17:32.790 --> 17:33.720
I was wrong.

17:36.880 --> 17:37.720
And you,

17:38.590 --> 17:39.480
Tian Xing,

17:39.920 --> 17:41.320
this is the Qi Residence,

17:41.730 --> 17:43.450
not the wild countryside.

17:44.480 --> 17:45.500
Look at you.

17:46.160 --> 17:48.440
How many lifetimes of fortune
did you cultivate

17:48.440 --> 17:51.040
to pass the Nine Cities'
scholar examination?

17:51.680 --> 17:54.480
Don't get expelled
for lacking proper etiquette!

17:55.120 --> 17:56.450
I will keep that in mind.

18:00.430 --> 18:02.390
Women and children,

18:02.410 --> 18:03.680
this year is truly absurd.

18:03.680 --> 18:05.280
It's more like a temple fair.

18:08.680 --> 18:09.350
Alright.

18:09.720 --> 18:11.980
Now, everyone comes up one by one in order

18:12.000 --> 18:13.480
to receive your assignments.

18:13.480 --> 18:14.510
Yes.

18:38.040 --> 18:38.840
Boqin.

18:38.860 --> 18:39.730
Yes.

18:39.760 --> 18:41.280
Your assignment is

18:41.350 --> 18:42.880
to inventory the tributes.

18:43.510 --> 18:44.440
Yes. I accept.

18:47.800 --> 18:48.910
You two,

18:49.030 --> 18:51.030
being late on your first day of probation,

18:51.030 --> 18:52.990
have no sense of time.

18:53.750 --> 18:56.500
It's clear you're both
unsuited for officialdom.

18:56.500 --> 18:59.000
Now that everyone has
received their assignments.

18:59.000 --> 19:01.440
The only things left are
organizing the library miscellany

19:01.440 --> 19:02.900
and cleaning the latrine.

19:03.480 --> 19:05.000
Choose between yourselves.

19:05.000 --> 19:06.680
-I'll clean the latrine.
-I'll clean the latrine.

19:06.680 --> 19:08.410
You're fighting over this too?

19:09.070 --> 19:10.530
Listen to my arrangement.

19:10.750 --> 19:11.510
Tian Xing,

19:12.110 --> 19:13.770
you organize the miscellany.

19:13.790 --> 19:15.520
Fan Yun, you clean the latrine.

19:17.510 --> 19:18.270
Yes.

19:19.880 --> 19:21.510
Dismissed. Go get to work.

19:23.160 --> 19:24.290
Let's go, Tian Xing.

19:32.150 --> 19:33.480
Back to the old trade, huh?

19:33.480 --> 19:34.480
But cleaning here

19:34.480 --> 19:37.680
is still better than cleaning
in the countryside, right?

19:38.030 --> 19:39.030
-You...
-Fan Yun.

19:40.400 --> 19:41.460
Peace and harmony.

19:47.000 --> 19:49.530
Peace and harmony, peace and harmony.

19:49.640 --> 19:50.510
Brother Bo,

19:50.530 --> 19:51.940
please look after us

19:52.480 --> 19:54.730
in the future.

19:54.880 --> 19:55.610
Definitely.

20:05.520 --> 20:06.520
Don't worry.

20:06.640 --> 20:07.720
Peace and harmony.

20:08.400 --> 20:08.930
Let's go.

20:10.170 --> 20:13.110
[Juyun Pavilion]

20:18.390 --> 20:19.110
Boss.

20:19.130 --> 20:21.930
The Ceremony Bureau sent
another purchase order.

20:28.590 --> 20:30.680
Get the goods from the shops
according to the list.

20:30.680 --> 20:31.240
Yes.

20:32.470 --> 20:33.070
Boss,

20:33.400 --> 20:37.000
the Ceremony Bureau is demanding
an extra ten percent kickback.

20:39.110 --> 20:40.040
What do you mean?

20:40.210 --> 20:42.380
They have repeatedly hinted to me

20:42.410 --> 20:43.740
that by always favoring our business,

20:43.740 --> 20:45.720
they've drawn attention of the higher-ups.

20:45.720 --> 20:47.750
They say if we want to
continue working together,

20:47.750 --> 20:50.880
we'll have to raise the kickback
by another ten percent.

20:53.480 --> 20:54.710
They're squeezing

20:55.120 --> 20:56.630
every last penny out of us.

20:56.880 --> 20:58.350
Truly insatiable greed.

20:59.540 --> 21:01.070
You are wise, Young Master.

21:01.400 --> 21:03.000
Then about the kickbacks...

21:03.640 --> 21:06.160
Juyun Pavilion became the largest
business alliance in Ling'an,

21:06.160 --> 21:08.550
and indeed in all Nine Cities,

21:09.240 --> 21:11.370
not by being bullied into submission.

21:11.460 --> 21:12.510
Tell them this:

21:13.070 --> 21:14.400
If they want a kickback,

21:14.450 --> 21:16.680
we can no longer guarantee
the quality of goods.

21:16.680 --> 21:19.310
If anything goes wrong,
they'll still have to take responsibility.

21:19.310 --> 21:20.910
You are right, Young Master.

21:21.110 --> 21:21.960
But,

21:21.960 --> 21:23.690
if we don't meet their demands,

21:24.000 --> 21:24.830
I'm afraid

21:24.830 --> 21:26.880
our business with them won't last long.

21:26.880 --> 21:27.940
It doesn't matter.

21:28.240 --> 21:29.480
The prices we offer are already

21:29.480 --> 21:30.920
the lowest on the market.

21:31.680 --> 21:33.880
It's never been about them choosing us.

21:34.000 --> 21:36.260
It's that they have no one else to choose.

21:37.250 --> 21:38.510
Asking for kickbacks?

21:39.030 --> 21:42.090
They're not in a position
to blackmail Juyun Pavilion.

21:43.050 --> 21:43.630
Understood.

21:43.630 --> 21:44.440
I

21:44.460 --> 21:46.190
will go reply to them right now.

21:47.030 --> 21:47.750
Wait.

21:50.830 --> 21:51.830
Is Fan Yun

21:52.810 --> 21:54.680
on probation at the Ceremony Bureau?

21:54.680 --> 21:58.080
I heard all the new scholars
are doing their probation there.

22:00.880 --> 22:01.940
Then the kickbacks

22:01.950 --> 22:03.190
can be negotiable.

22:05.240 --> 22:06.400
But tell them

22:07.150 --> 22:10.080
to make sure Fan Yun
receives the best possible care.

22:28.540 --> 22:30.630
If you really think this

22:30.680 --> 22:32.610
will make me lose heart and give up,

22:33.370 --> 22:35.290
then you are dead wrong.

22:37.490 --> 22:38.490
Just wait and see.

22:39.000 --> 22:41.790
I will clean this place until it shines.

22:41.790 --> 22:42.750
I will make you all

22:42.750 --> 22:44.240
look at me in a new light.

22:53.810 --> 22:54.880
Governor,

22:54.900 --> 22:56.360
is this really necessary?

23:09.790 --> 23:10.920
What are you doing?

23:10.920 --> 23:12.180
I'm sorry. Brother Bo.

23:12.680 --> 23:14.140
You came at the right time.

23:14.160 --> 23:16.020
I just finished cleaning inside.

23:16.040 --> 23:16.960
Please.

23:17.590 --> 23:18.640
Who is your Brother?

23:18.640 --> 23:19.590
Are you blind?

23:22.640 --> 23:25.040
Fan Yun indeed grew up
among the commoners.

23:25.070 --> 23:26.310
In such an awkward situation,

23:26.310 --> 23:28.170
she can still handle it with ease.

23:28.200 --> 23:29.400
I'd rather she didn't

23:30.510 --> 23:32.440
have to face situations like this.

23:33.350 --> 23:34.720
Go do what you need to do.

23:34.720 --> 23:35.980
Don't just stand here.

23:41.960 --> 23:42.920
You, get out quickly.

23:42.920 --> 23:44.980
With you here, how am I supposed to...

23:45.240 --> 23:45.960
Oh, right.

23:46.640 --> 23:47.310
Get out.

23:47.330 --> 23:47.840
Get out.

23:47.860 --> 23:48.680
Okay.

23:48.850 --> 23:50.440
I'll get out right now.

23:50.470 --> 23:51.270
Going out now.

24:37.240 --> 24:38.000
What is this?

24:39.600 --> 24:41.180
I specially placed this here,

24:41.180 --> 24:43.780
a bronze mirror
for tidying one's appearance.

24:44.160 --> 24:45.220
What's this smell?

24:46.440 --> 24:48.110
It's the scent of white orchids.

24:48.110 --> 24:49.310
With this scent,

24:49.340 --> 24:50.930
the entire latrine

24:51.030 --> 24:52.630
will be filled with fragrance,

24:52.630 --> 24:54.400
and it will also soothe our moods.

24:54.400 --> 24:55.000
This

24:55.550 --> 24:57.350
is the latrine of the Ceremony Bureau,

24:57.350 --> 24:59.480
not your noble lady's boudoir.

24:59.960 --> 25:02.360
Stop cluttering it with this random stuff.

25:02.480 --> 25:03.410
Did you see that?

25:03.850 --> 25:05.310
What's with his attitude?

25:05.480 --> 25:07.280
Wait here. I'll go deal with him.

25:07.790 --> 25:08.620
Don't stop me!

25:08.680 --> 25:09.720
Calm down.

25:09.720 --> 25:10.640
Governor.

25:11.240 --> 25:12.470
You said it yourself,

25:12.840 --> 25:13.920
if Fan Yun

25:13.940 --> 25:15.480
can't handle this on her own,

25:15.480 --> 25:17.070
then no one will ever truly accept her.

25:17.070 --> 25:18.800
If you step in to defend her now,

25:19.310 --> 25:20.480
then Fan Yun's efforts

25:20.480 --> 25:22.280
efforts will all be for nothing.

25:44.200 --> 25:44.920
Fan Yun.

25:46.370 --> 25:47.840
-Go... Go... Go away!
-Uncle.

25:47.840 --> 25:48.850
Lord Yan Jiang.

25:48.880 --> 25:49.880
Uncle.

25:49.900 --> 25:51.020
Why are you here?

25:51.640 --> 25:53.040
How did you cut your hand?

25:53.920 --> 25:54.960
I'm fine.

25:55.400 --> 25:57.080
Is probation at the Ceremony Bureau
always this leisurely?

25:57.080 --> 25:58.490
Why are you wandering around?

25:58.490 --> 25:59.440
Hurry back to work.

25:59.440 --> 26:01.720
If I have the chance
to learn from Lord Yan,

26:01.720 --> 26:02.960
that would be great.

26:03.800 --> 26:05.490
Take care of your own business first.

26:05.490 --> 26:06.440
Go back to work immediately.

26:06.440 --> 26:06.960
Yes.

26:07.860 --> 26:08.470
Wait.

26:10.860 --> 26:11.620
Go ahead.

26:12.960 --> 26:14.130
You're a girl.

26:14.160 --> 26:16.560
How can they make you
clean a men's latrine?

26:17.310 --> 26:19.440
Lord Lu must have lost his mind.

26:20.840 --> 26:22.490
There are so many positions
in the Ceremony Bureau.

26:22.490 --> 26:24.040
Let's get you switched, come on.

26:24.040 --> 26:26.080
Uncle, precisely because of this,

26:26.200 --> 26:27.310
I have to prove

26:27.570 --> 26:28.560
that no matter what I do,

26:28.560 --> 26:29.660
I can do it well.

26:31.160 --> 26:31.840
No.

26:31.860 --> 26:32.390
Let's go.

26:33.040 --> 26:34.480
-Let's go.
-Lord Yan, help me stop him.

26:34.480 --> 26:35.290
Father.

26:35.560 --> 26:37.400
Since Fan Yun is now an official,

26:37.420 --> 26:39.680
don't treat her differently
based on gender.

26:39.680 --> 26:40.310
Furthermore,

26:40.310 --> 26:42.510
she is a probationary civil official
of the Ceremony Bureau.

26:42.510 --> 26:44.970
Whatever Lord Lu assigns her
is only proper.

26:46.250 --> 26:47.480
Yan Jiang, let me tell you.

26:47.480 --> 26:49.200
First of all, she is my niece.

26:49.270 --> 26:50.350
How can my niece do this kind of

26:50.350 --> 26:51.750
dirty and tiring work?

26:51.750 --> 26:52.310
Besides,

26:52.310 --> 26:53.070
how can a girl

26:53.070 --> 26:54.400
clean a men's latrine?

26:55.440 --> 26:55.970
Let's go.

26:56.350 --> 26:57.460
Father, you...

26:57.480 --> 26:58.890
You stay out of this!

26:58.920 --> 27:01.230
Uncle, please hear me out first.

27:01.270 --> 27:02.290
What is it now?

27:02.320 --> 27:04.240
Since I've chosen to be an official,

27:04.240 --> 27:05.350
I must walk this path

27:05.350 --> 27:06.910
all by myself.

27:07.310 --> 27:08.070
If

27:08.070 --> 27:09.830
I don't even follow these rules,

27:09.830 --> 27:10.890
then in the future,

27:10.920 --> 27:12.450
how can I be a good official?

27:16.350 --> 27:17.270
Still no.

27:18.180 --> 27:19.730
Uncle.

27:19.760 --> 27:21.000
Think about it.

27:21.030 --> 27:22.480
If you cannot sweep a single room,

27:22.480 --> 27:24.010
how can you sweep the world?

27:25.200 --> 27:27.030
Uncle.

27:27.030 --> 27:29.070
Uncle.

27:29.070 --> 27:31.000
That does make sense.

27:32.240 --> 27:33.380
How about this?

27:33.720 --> 27:34.650
You do it for now.

27:34.960 --> 27:36.400
But if anything feels wrong,

27:36.400 --> 27:37.790
tell me anytime.

27:37.790 --> 27:40.030
We will change your position immediately.

27:40.030 --> 27:41.070
Thank you, Uncle.

27:47.200 --> 27:48.530
Good thing you were here

27:48.720 --> 27:49.680
to remind me.

27:50.750 --> 27:51.550
Thanks.

27:55.510 --> 27:56.910
Let me ask you a question.

27:57.400 --> 27:58.030
Do you think Fan Yun

27:58.030 --> 27:59.720
can become a good official?

28:01.720 --> 28:03.920
Given Fan Yun's current situation,

28:04.790 --> 28:06.450
I think it's highly possible.

28:12.270 --> 28:13.310
Then it seems

28:14.010 --> 28:15.940
we can only let her fight on her own.

28:17.680 --> 28:18.760
That is true,

28:19.440 --> 28:20.810
but in daily life,

28:21.750 --> 28:23.280
you can still show her care.

29:13.030 --> 29:13.960
Tian Xing.

29:14.590 --> 29:15.990
Look at what you've done.

29:18.440 --> 29:19.100
Brother Bo.

29:19.620 --> 29:20.580
I'm so sorry.

29:20.610 --> 29:21.960
I... I just...

29:21.980 --> 29:23.590
You... You... You...

29:25.070 --> 29:26.710
A mere commoner dares

29:26.960 --> 29:29.310
to be so insolent, disgracing all decency!

29:29.310 --> 29:30.830
I won't just let this go.

29:31.550 --> 29:32.350
Yes, yes, yes.

29:32.680 --> 29:34.280
it's my fault, it's my fault.

29:35.330 --> 29:37.130
How would you like this settled?

29:37.490 --> 29:38.720
As long as it's within my power,

29:38.720 --> 29:39.650
I will do my best.

29:43.830 --> 29:44.720
You said it.

29:50.370 --> 29:51.170
Wipe it clean.

29:55.110 --> 29:55.830
This...

30:13.970 --> 30:16.180
[Latrine]

30:20.750 --> 30:21.510
Ridiculous.

30:22.200 --> 30:23.800
He's just a country bumpkin.

30:24.010 --> 30:25.370
Boqin is teasing him like this,

30:25.370 --> 30:26.830
and he's still so grateful.

30:26.830 --> 30:28.150
Is he an idiot?

30:28.850 --> 30:31.120
I heard Boqin brought another group over.

30:31.120 --> 30:32.390
Not only that,

30:32.470 --> 30:33.640
he even stepped right into the mud pit,

30:33.640 --> 30:35.140
and got his shoes all filthy,

30:35.140 --> 30:35.960
then made him wipe them again.

30:35.960 --> 30:37.540
How did he become the winner?

30:37.540 --> 30:39.390
Probably just dumb luck.

30:43.750 --> 30:45.280
What are you doing? Get out!

30:45.640 --> 30:46.700
Where is Tian Xing?

30:48.770 --> 30:49.450
Boqin.

30:50.410 --> 30:51.570
Your shoes,

30:51.640 --> 30:54.160
I'm afraid no amount of cleaning
will restore them to their former state.

30:54.160 --> 30:55.310
No way.

30:55.310 --> 30:56.460
You are the winner.

30:56.880 --> 31:00.210
How could the winner not even clean
a pair of shoes properly?

31:01.240 --> 31:02.070
All right.

31:03.550 --> 31:04.510
I'll do my best.

31:08.240 --> 31:09.240
This is bullying.

31:11.310 --> 31:12.090
Tian Xing.

31:12.320 --> 31:13.080
Boqin.

31:13.590 --> 31:14.240
Get up.

31:14.720 --> 31:15.640
What are you doing?

31:15.640 --> 31:16.440
Wiping shoes.

31:17.300 --> 31:19.100
You are perfectly capable.

31:19.130 --> 31:20.810
Why ask others to wipe your shoes?

31:20.810 --> 31:21.810
He does a good job.

31:22.200 --> 31:23.050
You...

31:27.530 --> 31:28.050
Fine.

31:29.590 --> 31:30.920
You want your shoes wiped, right?

31:30.920 --> 31:32.420
I'm the best at it.

31:32.640 --> 31:33.640
I'll do it for you.

31:33.680 --> 31:34.240
Let's go.

31:34.560 --> 31:35.680
Follow me to the latrine.

31:35.680 --> 31:37.270
-Let me wipe your shoes.
-Fan Yun.

31:37.270 --> 31:38.270
I... I will have them wiped right here.

31:38.270 --> 31:40.390
My shoes are all made of fine brocade.

31:40.640 --> 31:42.010
I can't wear any other shoes.

31:42.010 --> 31:43.680
You are obviously doing this on purpose

31:43.680 --> 31:45.480
to humiliate a fellow official.

31:45.850 --> 31:47.000
You, Boqin.

31:47.790 --> 31:48.790
It seems with you,

31:49.090 --> 31:50.440
there really is no way

31:50.510 --> 31:51.970
to keep peace and harmony.

31:55.460 --> 31:56.260
Just you wait.

31:56.920 --> 31:58.730
I've already informed Lord Lu of this.

31:58.730 --> 31:59.790
He'll be here soon.

32:00.160 --> 32:01.890
I wonder what Lord Lu will think

32:02.200 --> 32:03.660
when he sees you like this.

32:11.430 --> 32:12.760
What are you doing?

32:13.030 --> 32:14.830
What tricks are you playing now?

32:17.310 --> 32:17.960
Fan Yun.

32:18.350 --> 32:19.200
He looks like

32:19.520 --> 32:20.660
he's in pain.

32:21.190 --> 32:21.750
But...

32:22.400 --> 32:23.530
I'll go check on him.

32:36.770 --> 32:37.370
Tian Xing.

32:38.270 --> 32:39.030
He... He... He...

32:39.030 --> 32:40.290
What's wrong with him?

32:41.750 --> 32:42.960
This is

32:43.830 --> 32:45.510
stomach pain

32:46.710 --> 32:47.710
from overwork.

32:49.320 --> 32:50.850
You must stay up late often,

32:50.930 --> 32:52.460
and have an irregular diet.

32:53.030 --> 32:54.960
Do you still want to be an official?

32:55.400 --> 32:56.660
If I don't stay up late,

32:57.030 --> 32:59.290
and don't put in more effort than others,

32:59.790 --> 33:01.910
how can I ever stand equal
to Lord Yan Jiang?

33:01.910 --> 33:03.200
I don't need your fake kindness.

33:03.200 --> 33:03.960
Don't move.

33:15.170 --> 33:16.090
Tian Xing,

33:16.230 --> 33:17.430
what should we do now?

33:19.200 --> 33:19.660
Fan Yun,

33:20.110 --> 33:21.110
go to the kitchen.

33:21.240 --> 33:22.510
Get a piece of Chinese yam

33:22.510 --> 33:23.510
and some milk.

33:23.530 --> 33:24.500
Chinese yam and milk.

33:24.500 --> 33:25.040
Okay.

33:25.160 --> 33:26.160
I'll go right now.

33:27.720 --> 33:28.110
Lord Jiang.

33:28.110 --> 33:29.530
Where are you rushing to?

33:29.880 --> 33:31.110
Tian Xing told me to go to the kitchen

33:31.110 --> 33:32.770
for some Chinese yam and milk.

33:40.720 --> 33:41.370
Someone,

33:41.830 --> 33:43.310
help him over to rest.

33:45.030 --> 33:45.690
Lord Jiang.

33:47.640 --> 33:49.160
Be careful. Slow down.

33:51.000 --> 33:52.350
You know medicine?

33:53.880 --> 33:56.170
I read a few medical books
in my spare time.

33:56.170 --> 33:57.230
Just know a little.

33:58.790 --> 34:01.200
If you ever want to discuss
medicine further,

34:01.200 --> 34:03.860
feel free to come find me
at the Commerce Bureau.

34:04.370 --> 34:04.950
This...

34:05.580 --> 34:06.840
Thank you, Lord Jiang.

34:19.730 --> 34:21.170
Why isn't he waking up?

34:26.590 --> 34:28.699
Brother Bo ate Tian Xing's remedy
and passed out.

34:28.699 --> 34:30.360
Can Tian Xing even be trusted?

34:31.190 --> 34:31.920
I doubt it.

34:32.210 --> 34:33.500
Brother Bo has never liked him.

34:33.500 --> 34:34.699
Why would he save him?

34:35.230 --> 34:36.489
Then what should we do?

34:38.370 --> 34:38.760
Brother Bo.

34:38.760 --> 34:40.159
Brother Bo, are you okay?

34:40.650 --> 34:41.639
How do you feel?

34:41.909 --> 34:43.389
Tian Xing saved me again?

34:43.409 --> 34:43.929
Yes.

34:54.639 --> 34:55.590
Please.

35:02.160 --> 35:03.360
Let's sit over there.

35:03.380 --> 35:03.860
Okay.

35:09.510 --> 35:10.400
Sorry,

35:10.840 --> 35:12.240
we didn't save you a seat.

35:12.340 --> 35:13.540
Get out immediately.

35:13.550 --> 35:15.000
Get out quickly. Hurry up!

35:15.000 --> 35:17.000
Exactly, get out. Hurry up!

35:17.000 --> 35:18.330
What are you looking at?

35:18.510 --> 35:19.150
Why?

35:19.560 --> 35:20.690
Isn't this the place

35:20.800 --> 35:22.530
where we all eat together?

35:22.860 --> 35:24.050
Why can you come here

35:24.080 --> 35:25.030
and I can't?

35:25.190 --> 35:25.910
Because

35:26.230 --> 35:26.920
you

35:27.510 --> 35:28.630
stink too much.

35:29.280 --> 35:31.070
So this is the lack of manners from those

35:31.070 --> 35:32.800
who have never taken the exams?

35:33.020 --> 35:34.500
The smell on you

35:34.520 --> 35:36.240
makes people lose their appetite
for three days.

35:36.240 --> 35:36.960
Nonsense.

35:37.600 --> 35:41.250
Long in a fish market,
you don't smell the stench.

35:41.280 --> 35:41.880
Of course

35:41.880 --> 35:42.940
you can't smell it.

35:43.000 --> 35:44.410
But to us,

35:44.620 --> 35:47.580
-Tian Xing.
-it smells absolutely awful.

35:49.480 --> 35:50.110
I really don't know

35:50.110 --> 35:51.910
how you have the nerve to come in.

35:52.000 --> 35:52.920
If it were me,

35:53.440 --> 35:54.510
I'd be too ashamed.

35:55.210 --> 35:56.550
Why are you still hanging around?

35:56.550 --> 35:58.030
Leave quickly. Get out!

35:58.030 --> 35:59.510
Hurry up, out! out!

35:59.510 --> 36:00.800
Leave. Get going!

36:00.800 --> 36:02.440
Right, everyone? Get out!

36:03.400 --> 36:04.670
In that case,

36:05.510 --> 36:06.400
if you can't stand the smell,

36:06.400 --> 36:08.060
you'll just have to endure it.

36:11.510 --> 36:13.910
Are kings and nobles
born to their station?

36:14.230 --> 36:16.100
What makes you think a man's status

36:16.100 --> 36:17.500
is nobler than a woman's?

36:17.690 --> 36:19.710
And what makes you think a scholar's rank

36:19.710 --> 36:21.710
is nobler than a latrine cleaner's?

36:21.800 --> 36:23.130
If we follow your logic,

36:23.500 --> 36:25.160
you didn't even place in the top three,

36:25.160 --> 36:27.690
so what right do you have
to criticize others?

36:28.190 --> 36:28.790
Tian Xing.

36:29.030 --> 36:29.630
Let's sit.

36:29.960 --> 36:31.220
Who said you could sit?

36:31.400 --> 36:32.360
How can we eat with you here?

36:32.360 --> 36:34.490
Exactly, how dare you speak like that?

36:35.360 --> 36:36.590
Just eat your food.

36:37.280 --> 36:38.680
Enough with the chatter.

36:39.710 --> 36:42.110
One more word and you're disrespecting me.

36:47.960 --> 36:48.840
Move aside.

36:48.840 --> 36:49.710
Move now!

36:54.280 --> 36:55.410
Lord Lu has arrived.

36:59.550 --> 37:01.030
Lord Lu.

37:12.150 --> 37:13.280
Sit down, everyone.

37:13.590 --> 37:14.400
Yes.

37:20.190 --> 37:21.190
Serve the dishes.

37:36.670 --> 37:38.380
What kind of new dish is this?

37:39.630 --> 37:40.830
Wild vegetable buns.

37:41.320 --> 37:42.190
Lord Lu must be

37:42.190 --> 37:44.070
worried we're hungry

37:44.670 --> 37:46.090
and can't hold our liquor,

37:46.090 --> 37:47.690
so he's served food first for us

37:47.690 --> 37:48.890
to line our stomachs.

37:50.280 --> 37:51.990
How thoughtful of Lord Lu.

37:52.070 --> 37:53.000
First serving

37:53.000 --> 37:53.970
these buns,

37:54.190 --> 37:55.390
then the main course.

37:58.710 --> 37:59.500
Everyone.

38:00.670 --> 38:02.520
According to tradition,

38:02.960 --> 38:04.550
all newly selected scholars

38:04.550 --> 38:06.350
must come to the Food Department

38:06.630 --> 38:08.630
to eat a meal of wild vegetable buns.

38:09.150 --> 38:09.920
This is to show

38:09.920 --> 38:11.480
that we share the common people's food,

38:11.480 --> 38:13.800
and to remember hardship
while cherishing the sweet.

38:13.800 --> 38:15.760
When you become officials in the future,

38:15.760 --> 38:17.920
you must not forget this meal today.

38:18.840 --> 38:20.060
We become officials

38:20.360 --> 38:22.550
not to feast on delicacies ourselves,

38:23.000 --> 38:25.710
but to ensure that the people
under our governance

38:25.710 --> 38:27.240
have enough to eat and wear.

38:27.550 --> 38:29.020
The praise of the people

38:29.550 --> 38:31.840
is the finest feast under heaven.

38:33.630 --> 38:34.490
Begin the meal.

38:46.690 --> 38:47.890
Wild vegetable buns?

38:48.360 --> 38:50.490
What wild vegetables are they made of?

38:51.230 --> 38:52.560
It's shepherd's purse.

38:53.230 --> 38:55.550
Shepherd's purse usually grows
between rivers

38:55.550 --> 38:56.810
and along field edges.

38:57.030 --> 38:59.360
It's known as the licorice of vegetables.

39:05.150 --> 39:06.030
You guys,

39:06.510 --> 39:08.170
what are you waiting for? Eat!

39:08.960 --> 39:10.150
Yes, yes, yes.

39:11.190 --> 39:13.250
What is this grayish thing?

39:13.610 --> 39:14.410
This

39:14.440 --> 39:15.700
might be dandelion.

39:16.150 --> 39:16.810
Dandelion?

39:17.790 --> 39:19.530
Buns made with shepherd's purse

39:19.530 --> 39:20.990
are really soft and tasty.

39:21.580 --> 39:23.140
After tasting carefully,

39:23.230 --> 39:25.030
there's also a faint fragrance.

39:25.790 --> 39:26.860
That fragrance

39:27.190 --> 39:28.650
mingled with

39:28.880 --> 39:30.680
the mellow flavor of dandelion.

39:31.290 --> 39:33.840
The shepherd's purse in this bun
should be grown locally.

39:33.840 --> 39:36.570
It seems this year's crops
are growing very well.

39:37.760 --> 39:40.180
How can you tell
the crop growth from this?

39:40.480 --> 39:41.760
You can determine the moisture content

39:41.760 --> 39:43.280
of shepherd's purse based on its texture,

39:43.280 --> 39:45.240
thereby gaining insight
into the year's rainfall conditions,

39:45.240 --> 39:46.770
and then draw conclusions.

39:46.850 --> 39:48.780
Lord Fan is indeed knowledgeable.

39:48.900 --> 39:51.100
Yes, I think so too.

39:51.140 --> 39:52.200
I tasted it as well.

39:52.340 --> 39:53.450
Yeah, yeah.

39:53.480 --> 39:55.210
I tasted it too.
